{"tid":45824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警長偷保釋金囚2年失長俸","createTime":"2016-12-19T08:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T10:16:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e4706464dfdcc2cebd26f9f96a3b42e3f41b561","tid":45824,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"灣仔警署今年5月發生「閉門失竊」案，存放在警署值日官夾萬內的107萬港元保釋金不翼而飛，負責保管夾萬匙的警長事後被指盜取該筆保釋金，被落案控以一項盜竊罪，涉案43歲被告張偉倫今在區域法院承認一項盜竊罪，判囚2年。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告案發當日為灣仔警署報案室值日官。當日上午11時，被告向同僚指自己相約朋友在警察總部飯聚而離去，一個多小時後，同僚接到被告的電話，被告在電話中無故為自己的行為道歉，及通知夾萬鎖匙在報案室的黑紙盒中。同僚其後已不能接觸被告，及發現夾萬內5包共107萬保釋金不翼而飛。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後調查得知被告向外欠債100萬港元。被告其後在內地自首，並於8月1日回港被捕。被告警誡下承認因欠債偷去款項，並想藉此作本在澳門贏回100萬港元來還債，他並在澳門丢棄其警察委任證。他指早於2009年便因他與妻輸錢、他自己投資失利而欠債。事發輸錢後，被告稱離開澳門時以為自己會被截停，怎料卻成功過關至珠海，他於是在內地自首。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告1992年加入警隊，2015年升為警長，月入3萬。辯方形容這是一宗悲劇，被告因財困欠債而犯案，卻因此摧毀其人生、職業生涯及家庭，他不但將失去長俸，且在他被捕不久，原以為會站在他一邊的妻子，卻要與他離婚，他為此而感到不開心，及已感到後悔。<br />\n<br />\n法官指案件雖令被告失去長俸等，但其犯案時應預計到後果。"},{"pid":"f0a06bfc8cb2259d440a845f0eb318a482854e85","tid":45824,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa5abd4a229f0a1cd94d36361107764dfef328d","tid":45824,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"今次唔算休班警。"},{"pid":"60de867ff013f94ee48869adfb09e3e62d53d3e8","tid":45824,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fbce5189455cd60a4ba69344af925f57f5e6cb","tid":45824,"uid":62668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"本人感到相當開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7b79de3e79e83c98e142b202c38cca54c7ca50","tid":45824,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249174625f3c513a5f3fbc6836189aeed8cb090d","tid":45824,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"咁嗰107萬要唔要嘔返出嚟？"},{"pid":"8e4990e7dd62fa2319d346873c0aed4dd8e10af6","tid":45824,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f968d54fd44e2612d89892223824ff461e3190ec","tid":45824,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"請人查哂家底財政學歷工作狀況<br />\n到頭有鬼用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10df6798c20d9978f1dc6f2f7fdec726f7a1bfb","tid":45824,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"黑警犯罪率會唔會高過普通市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31652bef451a1581616bb9dcbdf059a17b87b051","tid":45824,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次唔算休班警。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f54ec811e28d6be85a5866a2b68c8d50e23cea5","tid":45824,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"由97年/宣誓開始嘅人工都應該收返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df02e436f6bc17a583ddb3c37dc3a52b1a81ee7","tid":45824,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"休班警 VS 上班警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f86f683907c9172b9f0de3b2d4ab7f94fc2142","tid":45824,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":